00:01:26.599 --> 00:01:31.900
In the US alone, six in 10 adults
have a chronic illness.

00:01:31.924 --> 00:01:34.926
That's 125 million people.

00:01:35.830 --> 00:01:39.520
A recent report from
the Robert Wood Johnson Foundation

00:01:39.544 --> 00:01:44.607
showed that health habits
account for 50 percent

00:01:44.631 --> 00:01:46.924
of the health outcomes
that people experience,

00:01:46.948 --> 00:01:50.489
while medical care
only accounts for 20 percent.

